<view class="page"><view class="feedback-title"><text>问题和意见</text><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['chooseMsg',['$event']]]]]}}" class="feedback-quick" bindtap="__e">快速键入</text></view><view class="feedback-body"><textarea class="feedback-textare" placeholder="请详细描述你的问题和意见..." data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','content','$event',[]],['sendDate']]]]]}}" value="{{sendDate.content}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view><view class="feedback-title"><text>图片(选填,提供问题截图,总大小10M以下)</text></view><view class="feedback-body feedback-uploader"><view class="uni-uploader"><view class="uni-uploader-head"><view class="uni-uploader-title">点击预览图片</view><view class="uni-uploader-info">{{imageList.length+"/9"}}</view></view><view class="uni-uploader-body"><view class="uni-uploader__files"><block wx:for="{{imageList}}" wx:for-item="image" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><block><view class="uni-uploader__file" style="position:relative;"><image class="uni-uploader__img" src="{{image}}" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['previewImage',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e"></image><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['close',[index]]]]]}}" class="close-view" bindtap="__e">x</view></view></block></block><view hidden="{{!(imageList.length<8)}}" class="uni-uploader__input-box"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['uploadImage',['$event']]]]]}}" class="uni-uploader__input" bindtap="__e"></view></view></view></view></view></view><view class="feedback-title"><text>反馈类型</text></view><view class="feedback-body"><radio-group data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['handleFeedbackTypeChange',['$event']]]]]}}" class="feedback-type" bindchange="__e"><block wx:for="{{feedbackType}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><label class="feedback-type-item"><radio color="#fa436a" value="{{item.value}}" checked="{{item.value===sendDate.type}}"></radio><text>{{item.name}}</text></label></block></radio-group></view><view class="feedback-title"><text>QQ/邮箱/手机号</text></view><view class="feedback-body"><input class="feedback-input" placeholder="(选填,方便我们联系你 )" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','contact_way','$event',[]],['sendDate']]]]]}}" value="{{sendDate.contact_way}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['send',['$event']]]]]}}" class="feedback-submit" bindtap="__e">提交</button><view class="feedback-title"><text>反馈结果可在设置 -> 意见反馈 -> 点击列表后查看！</text></view></view>